    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ 425\u00b0F/ Gas 7</p><p>Cut\u00a0the<strong> potatoes</strong> (skins on) into wedges,\u00a0add them to a baking tray and drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until they're crisp</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/harissa-halloumi-sandwich-and-carrot-slaw/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel\u00a0then grate the <strong>carrots</strong> into a large mixing bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and a large drizzle of\u00a0<strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, mix well and set aside \u2013 this is your<strong> carrot slaw</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/harissa-halloumi-sandwich-and-carrot-slaw/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>halloumi</strong> in half lengthways (where the natural crease forms)</p><p>Add 500ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[800ml]\u00a0</span><strong>boiled water</strong> to a wide pot and return to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, carefully add the <strong>halloumi slices</strong> and boil for 5-8 min or until softened</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/harissa-halloumi-sandwich-and-carrot-slaw/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>ciabatta rolls</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until they're hot and crusty</p><p>While the ciabattas are toasting, chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Combine the <strong>harissa paste</strong> and<strong> mayo</strong> in a small bowl for serving \u2013 this is your <strong>harissa mayo</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/harissa-halloumi-sandwich-and-carrot-slaw/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, remove the <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>rolls</strong> from the oven and leave to cool before slicing in half</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and <strong>nigella seeds</strong> to the <strong>carrot slaw</strong> and give everything a good mix</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/harissa-halloumi-sandwich-and-carrot-slaw/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once softened, drain and pat the <strong>halloumi slices</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Using\u00a0a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, flatten and roll out each piece into a size similar to the ciabatta \u2013 these are your <strong>halloumi steaks</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/harissa-halloumi-sandwich-and-carrot-slaw/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the potato\u00a0wedges\u00a0are nearly cooked, heat a dry, non-stick pan over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi steaks</strong></p><p>Cook on each side for 1-2 min or until golden</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/harissa-halloumi-sandwich-and-carrot-slaw/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Spread each <strong>ciabatta base</strong> with the <strong>harissa mayo</strong>, then layer with the <strong>halloumi steaks</strong>, <strong>carrot slaw</strong>, and another dollop of <strong>harissa mayo</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>ciabatta lid</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>potato wedges</strong> and any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>carrot</strong> <strong>slaw </strong>and <strong>harissa</strong> <strong>mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
